91108100151/https://music.apple.com/gb/album/must-be-single/1485441230|archive-date=8 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 5 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 36\n|\n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''Big Conspiracy''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"No Denying\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/no-denying-single/1492144838|title=No Denying \u2013 Single by J Hus|website=iTunes|accessdate=3 January 2020}}</ref>\n| 33 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Repeat\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Koffee (singer)|Koffee]])</span>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2020\n| 21 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 64\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Play Play\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Burna Boy]])</span>\n| 11 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 38\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"8\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n====As a featured artist====\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of singles as a featured artist, showing year released, certifications and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UKchart\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br/><ref name=\"IREchart\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"So Paranoid\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/so-paranoid-feat-j-hus-single/1033241452|title=So Paranoid (feat. J Hus) \u2013 Single by Mostack|website=iTunes|accessdate=18 March 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404155038/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/so-paranoid-feat-j-hus-single/1033241452|archive-date=4 April 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br>{{small|([[Mostack]] featuring J 