 a ball, but 'Psycho Beach Party' must come to an end|url=http://www.nola.com/arts/index.ssf/1998/04/cast_had_a_ball_but_psycho_bea.html|work=[[The Times-Picayune]]|accessdate=24 October 2013|date=28 April 1998}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''At the Club Toot Sweet on Bourbon Street''\n| Cooch Deville\n| Southern Rep Theatre\n| rowspan=\"2\"|<ref name=\"stageclick\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''...And the Ball and All''\n| rowspan=\"2\"|Ernesto\n| North Star Theatre\n|-\n| 1999\n| Southern Rep Theatre\n|\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[Cabaret (musical)|Cabaret]]''\n| Emcee\n| [[Le Petit Theatre du Vieux Carre]]\n| <ref name=\"stageclick\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2003\n| ''Bianca's Remote Out of Control''\n| rowspan=\"2\"|Various roles\n| rowspan=\"2\"|Le Chat Noir\n| <ref>{{cite web|last=Sands|first=Brian|title=Oh La La\u2013Cabaret as Art: Bianca's Remote Out Of Control at Le Chat Noir|url=http://www.ambushmag.com/is103/trod.htm|work=Ambush Magazine|accessdate=24 October 2013|year=2003|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029185745/http://www.ambushmag.com/is103/trod.htm|archive-date=29 October 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Hollywood Heaven''\n| <ref>{{cite web|last=Shannon|first=Patrick|title=Camping With The Black Cat, Again!: A Revisit to Hollywood Heaven and The Black & White Blues|url=http://www.ambushmag.com/is2603/trod.htm|work=Ambush Magazine|accessdate=24 October 2013|date=2003|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195224/http://www.ambushmag.com/is2603/trod.htm|archive-date=29 October 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2004\n| ''[[Grease (musical)|Grease]]''\n| Vince Fontaine\n| Le Petit Theatre du Vieux Carre\n| rowspan=\"7\"|<ref name=\"stageclick\">{{cite web|title=Roy Haylock|url=http://www.stageclick.com/person/725.aspx|work=StageClick|accessdate=24 October 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Murder at Movary Manor''\n| Daphne\n| Marigny Theatre\n|-\n| ''[[The Bad Seed (play)|The Bad Seed]]''\n| Hortense Daigle\n| Le Chat Noir\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2005\n|